data.description: NEW LOWER PRICE11 THIS IS THE OPPORTYNITY YOU HAVE BEEN LOOKING! Located in one of the most convenient locations in Concord and minutes from Charlotte and Concord Mills, 2604 Brackley Place (off of Pitt School Road)  is a wonderful home that has been beautifully updated from top to bottom. This 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home features  1584 square feet with brand new kitchen quartz countertop and tile backsplash. The cabinets have been completely refinished with new up to date hardware..New sink and faucet, a new kitchen floor and a new sliding double door leading to the newly refinished patio. If ever a home is move-in ready , this is it!!Easy move in, easy maintenance and easy access. Who could ask for anything more!
